 the fixed node density and fixed coverage\ncase and by $\\Theta (E_t^{2/3})$ for the fixed per-node sensing energy and\nfixed density and increasing coverage case.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 9 Mar 2009 08:23:43 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-03-10"}
