ter transition, which is peculiarly manifested\nby the dispersionless peak, occurs only for those ensembles possessing the\nanisotropy strength in the region 1.0 <= D/J <= 5.0.....\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 9 Mar 2009 15:11:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-03-10"}
